00:04:18,424 --> 00:04:23,623
No, not even the renowned,
wise priest from Kiyomizu Temple

21
00:04:24,964 --> 00:04:28,195
has heard a story
as strange as this.

22
00:04:28,468 --> 00:04:32,666
Soyou know something
about this strange story?

